title: Online Dating Rituals Of The American Male S01E02 Brian Ephraim
description:
Brian, a 33 year-old playboy, has put walls up after a devastating breakup. This serial first-dater treats dating like a game as the countless women he meets online pale in comparison to his lost love. Ephraim, a 33 year-old single father, carries the weight of raising his young son and caring for his sick father all on his own.
